        "meta_description": "After a brutal year 2000 in which the The Learning Company was unceremoniously shed by Mattel and picked up by Gores Technology Group, the company has announced a new name for its entertainment division, now called &quot;Game Studios&quot;.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
